// SECTION 21 — WORLD-BUILD STUDIO
// [v2.46.0 STUDIO-SHELL-TEARDOWN] Formerly a full-screen overlay covering the
// whole character/world workspace (Wizard Chat, Entity Tabs + Generate Panel,
// Studio Rail nav, Image Gallery tab, Character Gallery grid + profile sheet).
// Everything except Wizard Chat (21a), the Image Gallery Tab (21d, now used by
